          <h4>Collect data</h4>
          <p>Use your smartphone to collect and update information in the field, log your current location, and put data you capture to work so you can make more informed and timely decisions. <br/>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/en/arcgis-online/use-maps/collect-data.htm" class="icon-right-arrow">&nbsp;Show me how</a></p>
            <br />
         
          <h4>Monitor dashboard view</h4>
          <p>Monitor activities and events, track your field workforce, and assess the status and performance of your daily operations.<br/>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/en/arcgis-online/use-maps/collect-data.htm" class="icon-right-arrow">&nbsp;Show me how</a></p>
<br />
          
          <h4>Get directions</h4>
          <p>Direction options include return to start and optimize the order. Once you get directions, you can zoom to the full route, print the directions, add the route as a layer to your map, and perform analysis on the route.<br/>
